thread.title: K. Kell
thread.title_full: Peaches Boutique reviewed by K. Kell

author: K. Kell
title: K. Kell
text: My daughter was looking for a particular prom dress and luck us, Peaches Boutique had it. I was very nervous about ordering a Prom Dress from out of state, however I ordered the Dress on Sunday evening(In Alabama) and we received the dress on Thursday evening. The dress was exactly what we were looking for and it was about $50 cheaper than other stores. Thanks Peaches Boutique :)
